column5: Hey Guys,  Just wondering if anyone from the board has ever made their way to this event??  http://www.eelpoutfestival.com/  Looks like an awesome time.
Looks awesome!  Too bad such a long drive.  Canadian dollar won't go far either!

Im going in 2017 I think  Gonna start building a custom hut this spring and pimp it out for the event hahaha  Anyone else interested in going??  Might be interesting to have an Ontario group there to show them how to "fish"!!!
I wonder if any alcohol is allowed? Looks like a large NWT town. And a blast. If it was 30 years ago I'm in.
Wow. I think for 2018 I'm in.
